title: Dragon Ball Z: Resurrection of F English Subtitles
description:
KP - Translatinons, Coding subs
Hop3 - Translations for part 2 & translation checks
Some guy 1 - Fixing some of the subtitle files
Kazenshuu.com - For providing the synopsis so I could check my work!

-------------------------------


Dragon Ball Z: Resurrection of F/ Fukkatsu no F/ La Ressurection de F

Coming at you with a brand spanking new subbed version of the new DBZ movie. This shit took a long time to do too.

The video is a cam rip of a spanish dub of the movie, and It's a pretty good quality, except for the few people that decided to talk during the movie.

Everything can be found in the files provided

Please enjoy!


**NOTE**
I'd like to point out, that this is the only version of the movie available right now, or I would have used a JPN rip, so please don't complain.


-------Credits and Thanks-------
 
Thank you to the anon that posted the videos in the first place! Without you, this project couldn't have even started!
Another shout out to the guys at kanzenshuu.com for the synopsis of the RoF movie. It helped a lot when I couldn't hear what characters were saying!
And a big THANK YOU to the person that actually recorded the movie! Its a pretty damn good cam rip!
Even more thanks to the anon that fixed some of the files!
Final thanks to the anon that merged all the .srt files together and created it for the whole movie! I know how long it takes to do that, and I really appreciated it!
